<h2 class="bold font-l">The Good, The Bad and The Ugly</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
$200,000 is a lot of money. Blondie, Tuco and Angel-Eyes are going to have to earn it. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MeleeATrois" class='trope-example-link'>Mle  Trois</a></p>
</div>
